function Start(sQuestName, sStepName, idActorPlayer)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_GUARD)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone) then
		Hydra.Wait(3)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorClone, true)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, LOC_GUARD_END, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONVO_GUARD, id_Self, actorClone, ID_HEALER)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_HEALER, CONVO_GUARD)
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorClone)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 0.3)
	end
	
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("Theater_End", idSelf, idSelf)
	
end
